What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Automated Hospital Beds Market?

Market Analysis and Size

In recent years, medical equipment such as hospital beds are in high demand in healthcare facilities, regardless of region or country. During the critical period when patients are hospitalized, beds must be designed to provide maximum comfort while also protecting them from external damage. Hospital beds are expected to be crammed with extra amenities that will supplement the patient's relief during the operation and recovery period 2023-2030.

Data Bridge Market Research analyses that the global automated hospital beds market which was USD 24.20 billion in 2022, is expected to reach USD 39.57 billion by 2030, and is expected to undergo a CAGR of 6.34% during the forecast period 2023-2030. This indicates that the market value. “Fully Automatic” dominates the type segment of the global automated hospital beds market. Rising innovations and advancements in medical device technology, combined with an increasing patient pool, are driving the increase in demand for automated hospital beds. In addition to the insights on market scenarios such as market value, growth rate, segmentation, geographical coverage, and major players, the market reports curated by the Data Bridge Market Research also include depth expert analysis, patient epidemiology, pipeline analysis, pricing analysis, and regulatory framework.

